# Quiet CycloneDX's bundled JSON-schema validator: it logs WARN "Unknown keyword
# meta:enum / deprecated" because it doesn't recognize some CycloneDX 1.6 schema
# keywords — cosmetic, and cyclonedx-maven-plugin has no skip-validation flag.
# `error` keeps genuine validation errors visible; it only drops the keyword WARNs.
-Dorg.slf4j.simpleLogger.log.com.networknt.schema=error
